N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 11, ch. III, subch. B, pt. 63 - Reserve Requirements For Financial Guaranty Insurance In-force Prior To The Effective Date Of Article 69 Of The Insurance Law

State Regulations
§ 63.0 - Preamble
§ 63.1 - Reserve requirements for financial guaranties in force prior to may 14, 1989 for insurers not authorized to write financial guaranty insurance pursuant to section 6902 of the insurance law
§ 63.2 - Reserve requirements for financial guaranties written prior to and in force as of july 1, 1989 for financial guaranty insurance corporations authorized pursuant to section 6902 of the insurance law
§ 63.3 to 63.4 - [Repealed]
§ 63.5 - [Repealed]
Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 11, ch. III, subch. B, pt. 63

Statutory authority: Insurance Law, §§ 201, 301, 6903[a], 6907[b], art. 69
